{"tid":1549512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，你地究竟係咪真係有抗爭嘅覺悟？","createTime":"2019-09-07T10:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T09:52:32.000Z","uid":22607,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8e0f86980c913f9d21c042424c3f33098b2984df","tid":1549512,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:47:47.000Z","msg":"又係我，機場撚一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日大家都見到<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地大部分人都做到旅客裝，唔叫口號，唔帶gear同唔set roadblock</span><br />\n縱使啲狗逐架A車查，都感覺到佢地好撚捉蟲<br />\n所以係之後嘅機場行動，上面四個戰術都係有成效同必須keep<br />\n<br />\n但係今日嘅行動依然有好大缺陷<br />\n我想係到檢討下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">首先，最大嘅缺陷係<br />\n我地今日人數完全不足</span></strong></span><br />\n經歷過812機場還眼嘅手足都知，個日係好撚多人<br />\n多到企都冇位企，巴士都上唔到<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但係今日，基本上係所有A車都坐唔滿<br />\n機場快綫都冇乜人去搭</span><br />\n有人話，因為啲狗停晒E車，A車又逐架上去查，咁好驚，就唔出啦<br />\n或者，有人話，上次大散水，唔想再行公路幾個鐘，唔出黎啦。<br />\n<br />\n我想講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇搞錯？乜宜家唔係抗爭緊咩？<br />\n如果連搭車都驚比人查同check id，咁你地究竟有冇做好為自由而戰嘅覺悟？</span></span><br />\n愈少人出黎，機場同巴士嘅手足就愈危險<br />\n今日冇出黎嘅人，對唔對得住之前被捕嘅手足？對唔對得住機場手足？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">機場手足都係手足，唔係condom。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二點就係，我個人認為<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好再係東涌搭巴士去機場</strong></span></span><br />\n雖然黑狗停晒E車<br />\n但仲有A車係可以由市區直接搭到機場巴士總站<br />\n東涌地勢實在係好不利，黨鐵一封東涌站就好撚大獲<br />\n你見佢地今日調派警力去東涌係好撚快<br />\n但機場唔同，佢地真係暫時都未敢係機場打鳩我地（黑警底線以後唔知）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果有狗黎，我地堅持等巴士，堅持自己會走，有巴士就會走，千其唔好大散水行公路</span><br />\n<br />\n都係個句，我講嘅可能都唔啱<br />\n大家一齊檢討<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n聽日美領見</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0692c8ba81c4cec0f225e0e7f06171892b1c2235","tid":1549512,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:49:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0ac6d5e4c21dfbf2f35b1070ee26b5b2f16afa8","tid":1549512,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:49:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9a2adc3c45c095e5df2634071bc204bd9e777a9","tid":1549512,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:49:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"199a27c2e61c7af1ad1bffb9f44bd4f1e7a9e723","tid":1549512,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:50:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bc652372e36d50d0191a0675ea0d040c943d24f","tid":1549512,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:50:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"429d6e8328a6ae8e223d3c827244f7627067aa92","tid":1549512,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:51:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9369f4423860320756b0cfdb3408f1e0a4f15a5","tid":1549512,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:52:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83496a849f1b1bc8fe4f8645c06c3457326588b7","tid":1549512,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:52:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"808a12319d1b9a5aeedbca984b4560e7d8ec398a","tid":1549512,"uid":300697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:53:05.000Z","msg":"大家都好累，加上文宣戰失焦⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n集中力量和理非各區聲討警暴！"},{"pid":"fe66f6bd9802981778285cc9cc1b75d6a0d999c2","tid":1549512,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:53:27.000Z","msg":"推^_^"},{"pid":"32a7994bd51d6a2a74a6c82c845ed4bfd5433ac3","tid":1549512,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:54:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2aadaa40a3d873a68bd5ac2cf744d9e1f3e7150b","tid":1549512,"uid":159596,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:58:08.000Z","msg":"民氣已經散散地<br />\n個個ig開po講好嬲好嬲又一日<br />\n<br />\n罷工驚炒<br />\n搭車驚被人check<br />\n黑衫唔敢